Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真不該畫畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,請問這是美術社的部長該說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,總之在宇佐美來到前  清理好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不然她可是會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我想確認一下  這幅畫是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這是宇佐美同學的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:55.15,Comment,,0,0,0,,但是瑞瑞不是很高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:56.25,Comment,,0,0,0,,誰在高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.64,Comment,,0,0,0,,你看起來就是很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拖延時間  你來想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:00.84,Comment,,0,0,0,,你們快點給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.90,Comment,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷  你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是宇佐美同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,居然在這種地方遇見  真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是活動室門前  會遇到很正常吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼奇怪的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  你杵在那裡我進不去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不  這該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太可疑了  快讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,部長  你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要是一站起來  肯定就會穿幫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要是穿幫的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法  就算是猴戲也得參與了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我不想讓宇佐美同學看到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是顏料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,部長你真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇了我一大跳  太惡趣味了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,別裝了  部長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你要睡到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜一下  先冷靜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是凶器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是已經被犯人拿走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,現場並沒有發現類似的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,還打算繼續演嗎  不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,保護現場是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要踏入被害人的周邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想玩凶殺推理遊戲的話  就請你們兩個人玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我還要把自己的畫的最後一道工序畫完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因為比賽的截止時間就是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:04:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明天!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不參加點這類比賽活動的話  我們這社團就會被解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,解散!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道放在這裡的那幅畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不  沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,話說  書架子上好像有畫布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是可蕾特同學放的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道那個人有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是在更裡面一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你就找一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,更裡面?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,部長  部長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,比起這個  現在有緊急狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我想上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在寫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,比起那些  先讓我上廁所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,給我憋住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡不需要插畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的有看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡  在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我看到的是妳的內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這不就是公主抱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在最後會被公主抱  還會得到親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,深情長吻!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss  Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:48.55,Comment,,0,0,0,,Kiss…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你們快走開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,部長  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,撞到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不  是被宇佐美的畫插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛剛說了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話  比賽就用內卷的畫來湊合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我重要的老婆居然要拿去供人觀賞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,會得獎的作品才會拿出來展示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,總之事情就這樣決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就是就是  居然不是金獎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,從…從什麼時候開始喜歡上內卷的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,妳想  晚上在朋友家留宿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,對姊妹淘睡前話怎能不談戀愛的話題嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,說嘛  怎麼喜歡上內卷的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不提也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不想說  那也可以聊聊這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明藏起來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,說吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不會笑我?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不笑你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,開始對他有好感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是在去年的十一月左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  內卷他剛入部的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  內卷!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是你把這裡的顏料全都用光的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.60,Comment,,0,0,0,,也不是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:15.95,Comment,,0,0,0,,這些是大家共用的顏料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.97,Comment,,0,0,0,,至少打一聲招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢…算是關係不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  用了這些我才能畫出這麼多老婆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,部長  我現在能去買些新顏料嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,還有什麼需要順便捎來的東西嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沙發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,睡椅子實在是背痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不需要這種助長偷懶風氣的用品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來  最近這一帶似乎有可疑人物出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  內卷  你就跟她一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧  又沒什麼必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因為內卷看上去那麼孱弱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真是沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,胳膊好細!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  這就回家了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是第一次見到這位吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我美術社的顧問  小山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,年齡雖大  但我叫小山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一年級四班的內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我們想出去買顏料之類的用品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那你們好好相處  注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,買得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一次性買好才更輕鬆吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你也替我這個搬運工想想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,男生做這點小事不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀煩人  所以說這三次元的女生就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那個  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你們看見過一個四歲左右的小女孩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小女孩?  沒看見過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,出什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,事情是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我離開了一小會兒  回來後就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,外貌特徵如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大概有這麼高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,偏長的頭髮在身後紮成了麻花辮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,穿著白色線衫  背著心形的包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,名字叫萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,萌香!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可疑人物…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直可疑!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這個應該不是傳聞中的那個可疑人物吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷  看那人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,四歲左右  麻花辮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,白色線衫  心形包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對  就是那個迷路的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  這包真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不過是個書包而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在和這小女孩說話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你叫萌香對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就和姐姐一起去媽媽那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,給我等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你們真是很可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你才可疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就是傳聞中的可疑人物吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可疑人物?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就是壞人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,壞…人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  別亂說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.72,Comment,,0,0,0,,藉口就免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細想想 「你媽媽在找你呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這種話根本就是拐騙犯的常用伎倆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是五點半
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,各位小學生請立刻回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,得回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,回我的星球去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:12:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不跟壞人走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只是她搞錯了而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼連你也跟著哭起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你看著就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快看  這是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  哥哥你是媽媽的朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以和我一起去媽媽那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥你畫得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥我可是美術社的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,美術社?  這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是能畫很多可愛女生的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  根本莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哼哼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,還哼哼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,三次元女生就算這麼做也根本就不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,沒讓你多嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事過後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就開始覺得他也並不是個壞心腸的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,羞死人了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HF0E5D4&\b0\pos(234.642,331.072)\frz296.4}怎麼感覺\N有點冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HF0E5D4&\b0\frz22.65\pos(238.071,365.356)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?  情…情書?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我收到了一封情書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今早來上學時發現它就在鞋櫃裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,部長你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,閃瞎眼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷的現充氣場實在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是與現充無緣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這話該由本人說嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  同時有多名女生傾心於你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這不就已經是現充的表現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,多名?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只拿到一封情書而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  我這麼說是因為還有其他女生喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯吧  宇佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你把情書帶來這裡是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,炫耀?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想問問怎麼處理這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼偏偏就找我商量了  求放過!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次收到情書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  是嗎!  哦  是嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,順便一問  宇佐美同學你寫過類似的東西嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒寫過吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛…這件事用不著你操心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天我以牙還牙秀你一臉的  做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼  你別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,比  比起那種事  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該會好好回覆人家的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那是當然的  畢竟這是禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經決定好要怎麼回覆了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我打算這麼回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回答?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,掂量掂量自己的斤兩  你這三次元的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你那個絕對不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  這樣不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你那會對人家造成心靈創傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來以為這算是委婉表現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一點都不委婉  太直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說你要拒絕對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是理所當然的嗎  對方可是三次元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,請你稍微按照常理來思考一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你說我?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你才更應該按照常理來拒絕人家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,舉例來說  是什麼樣的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,舉例來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,學長已經有其他喜歡的人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經有喜歡的角…已經有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他剛剛絕對是要說「喜歡的角色」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  結果他算是用了老套的拒絕方式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟他也不是說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,學長  你喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這所學校的女生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好像開始被對方刨根究底地問了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說他是變態這件事已經暴露了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先答應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,先答應吧  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,果然  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡的人是宇佐美學姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你們二位總是在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就想你說的喜歡的人會不會是指宇佐美學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,給我答應…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,目的都變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不  跟宇佐美半毛錢關係都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我還覺得肯定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭啦  真的不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我和宇佐美同學只是社團朋友關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧宇佐美同學的建議才得以順利拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好  明天也要鼓起幹勁來畫老婆了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,總之  算是維持現狀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?  好可愛?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全一見鍾情了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙畫的老婆很多都是幼女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就想他會不會是蘿莉控
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就乾脆直接問他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然後?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能呢  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真把小學生當作老婆  那可是變態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那畫就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,傳聞中也有那種會不知不覺間越陷越深的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說  內卷會不知不覺間就變成蘿莉卷也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來  內卷對4歲的女孩子很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會真的是蘿莉卷…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,誒嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學你有看見剛剛那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那個手機吊帶真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,果然你看上的是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  總算是放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,被擊沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說  千佳碰上可怕的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,被怪人緊盯著不放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎麼回事  必須得通報警方才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,穿著帶帽上衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,胸口上有星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,其他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一頭茶髮  還默默偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那絕對是個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,其他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,穿著和姐姐一樣的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?  同一所學校的變態?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是內卷學長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.37,0:23:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭  我沒有那麼厲害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有這張照片就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不會飛的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,機會主義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.35,0:23:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是部長卻這麼沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在我心目中對你們的信任正在動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,魔術秀時間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,已經夠辛苦的了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你總算茁壯成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  這個美術社大有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要找的東西是波波Kiss  敬請期待
